p: The oxygenated hydrocarbons with a small ratio of 3.33% of the total mass were also characterized. Only four compounds were identified as oxygenated hydrocarbons, including 6,10,14-trimethyl-2-pentadecanone (1.23%) as a major, while cis-13,16-docasadienoic acid (0.52%) was detected as a minor compound.
